{"tid":1068824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日大愚係香港底線","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:59:14.000Z","uid":185121,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb0b283c43e4436720a6e06d50c57adc6650c77","tid":1068824,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"乜乜乜係香港底線呢啲咁既口號成日都見，但每次都係比人踩完線之後又搬多條再低啲既底線出嚟。<br />\n條條都係底線，然後比人踩完又乜反抗都冇，香港人根本就冇底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日諗住中共遲早有報應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港比人滅咗嗰陣都未必到佢呀，報應。<br />\n香港人依家就係報應嘞，比人又打唔掙扎，真係比人打死都抵。攬炒啦香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話雖然係咁講，但其實我都乜都做唔到。口話想反抗，但香港人返工都返到乜都唔想做啦，話唔定真係要失業潮先會選擇抗爭(前題係香港人唔選擇自殺"},{"pid":"20783ae7a3b72fb610b8c556c8ede7f5b1beedbf","tid":1068824,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"執笠清貨 最後一日<br />\n但日日都係最後一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7891d239967d8e1073c721d7647ddb418dab2414","tid":1068824,"uid":185121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20783ae7a3b72fb610b8c556c8ede7f5b1beedbf","tid":1068824,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"執笠清貨 最後一日<br />\n但日日都係最後一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係囉 等到地主加租加到自己賣身跳樓都唔掂咪摺埋囉"},{"pid":"67cecb7b3bdadd84ea80dfeaed21d8d3157e1feb","tid":1068824,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FseT2No.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFseT2No.gif&h=892214a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb62478d1bcba41ff1a2b51a1b324af5b683ade0","tid":1068824,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco