03-19T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"其實點都死，一係比人人格抹殺，一係比人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108361325041063d96d2a4d0297bb4148797c77f","tid":1068824,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:43:58.000Z","msg":"人人都知 但係乜都做唔到 早走早著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564f036015bccb205cee46f2f7ba60779258fb3f","tid":1068824,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"我見到屋企兩老已經覺得冇得救，今日我老母仲大大聲聲話中國同古中國唔同既話，佢就係漢人而我就係南蠻喎。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我呀婆同我呀爺兩邊都係本地人後代，我都唔明白點生得佢哋兩個奶共仔出嚟。"},{"pid":"8561dfca7dd2ce082afe1324eda2c295815b00cf","tid":1068824,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"明日大愚唔起<br />\n班藍領冇工開<br />\n個個地盤佬今次開心囉<br />\n日日有鐵扎<br />\n日日有板釘<br />\n佢地理撚得你起咩尻<br />\n最緊要有錢收<br />\n啲白海豚死撚曬關香港人地撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正遲早都會死<br />\n呢家死起碼死係香港人手中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係笑撚死<br />\n我都係時候要做地盤真漢子<br />\n一個明日大愚<br />\n夠扎到我退休<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}